ith alerts. Your AI agent, the one you've been so proud of for optimizing cloud infrastructure costs, just decided to scale your Kubernetes cluster to 500 nodes. The monthly cost? $60,000. The reason? A traffic spike that lasted all of 90 seconds."]}],["$","br","4",{}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["This isn't a hypothetical scenario. It happened to us six months ago, and it's what inspired the creation of Vienna OS, the governance platform we're open-sourcing today."]}],["$","br","6",{}],["$","h2","7",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"The Illusion of AI Safety"}],["$","br","8",{}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["When most people think about AI safety, they picture guardrails: systems that filter outputs, detect harmful content, or prevent models from generating inappropriate responses. But it completely falls apart when AI agents can take autonomous actions in the physical world."]}],["$","br","10",{}],["$","p","11",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*Output-level safety (Guardrails):*"}],["$","li","12",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"AI generates a response → Safety filter reviews → Approved response displayed"}],["$","li","13",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Timeline: Reactive (after generation)"}],["$","li","14",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Stakes: Reputation, user experience"}],["$","br","15",{}],["$","p","16",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*Execution-level governance (What we actually need):*"}],["$","li","17",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"AI decides on action → Governance system evaluates → Action executed if approved"}],["$","li","18",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Timeline: Proactive (before execution)"}],["$","li","19",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Stakes: Business continuity, legal compliance, financial loss"}],["$","br","20",{}],["$","h2","21",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Enter Execution Warrants"}],["$","br","22",{}],["$","p","23",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["We call it ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"execution warrants"}],"—a concept borrowed from law enforcement and adapted for autonomous systems."]}],["$","br","24",{}],["$","p","25",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Instead of AI agents executing actions directly, they submit ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"execution intents"}]," to a governance control plane. This system validates, evaluates, classifies risk, and issues cryptographically signed warrants for approved actions."]}],["$","br","26",{}],["$","h3","27",{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"The Four Risk Tiers"}],["$","br","28",{}],["$","p","29",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"T0 (Minimal Risk)"}]," - Auto-approve"]}],["$","li","30",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Health checks, read operations, status queries"}],["$","br","31",{}],["$","p","32",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"T1 (Moderate Risk)"}]," - Single operator approval"]}],["$","li","33",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Routine deployments, configuration changes"}],["$","br","34",{}],["$","p","35",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"T2 (High Risk)"}]," - Multi-party approval + MFA"]}],["$","li","36",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Financial transactions, data deletion, major infrastructure changes"}],["$","br","37",{}],["$","p","38",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"T3 (Critical Risk)"}]," - Board-level approval"]}],["$","li","39",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"Actions that could impact business continuity"}],["$","br","40",{}],["$","h2","41",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Real-World Impact: Six Months of Production Use"}],["$","br","42",{}],["$","p","43",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*Incidents Prevented:*"}],["$","li","44",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"1 potential $60K infrastructure scaling error"}],["$","li","45",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"3 unauthorized database modifications"}],["$","li","46",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"5 financial transactions flagged for additional review"}],["$","br","47",{}],["$","p","48",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"*Operational Metrics:*"}],["$","li","49",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"99.7% uptime across all governed systems"}],["$","li","50",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"<50ms added latency for T0/T1 actions"}],["$","li","51",{"className":"text-slate-300 ml-4 text-sm","children":"100% audit trail completeness for SOC 2 examination"}],["$","br","52",{}],["$","hr","53",{"className":"border-navy-700 my-8"}],["$","br","54",{}],["$","p","55",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"Vienna OS is the governance layer agents answer to. Get started free →"}],["$","br","56",{}]]}],["$","$Lf",null,{"slug":"why-ai-agents-need-governance"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12","children":["$","$L10",null,{"variant":"compact","showSocialProof":true,"clas